The channel-id remapping approach (matching a HDHomeRun device's tuner lineup
to SiliconDust's cloud XMLTV feed by display name) follows the same approach
as IncubusVictim's HDHomeRunEPG-to-XmlTv (GPL) Python script, reimplemented
independently in C# as a native Jellyfin plugin; no code from that project is
reused or redistributed.

